programme.desc: The Ming Emperor Zhengde flees the palace to see the world after his mother orders him to marry an ugly princess. He disguises as a commoner and escapes with his advisors, but a gambling mishap causes them to part ways and Zhengde lost all his money. Phoenix, the owner of Lung Fung Inn, takes him in out of pity, and thus begins his new adventure...

programme.title: Raging Fire
programme.desc: As the police sets to arrest a drug lord, a team of masked thugs steals the drugs and murders the cops. Inspector Bong is devastated to see the aftermath of the carnage and soon discovers that the killers are led by Ngo, a former fellow cop who was forced into a life of crime by him. As the two men meet again, it is time to settle the score…

programme.title: Far Far Away
programme.desc: A 28-year-old IT geek has only been in love once. Surprisingly, he ends up getting romantically involved with five different women this year and the one thing they have in common is that they all live in far flung areas of Hong Kong. After taking five intensive relationship courses within these 365 days, will he find “the-one”?

programme.title: The White Storm 2: Drug Lords
programme.desc: In this epic action-thriller starring Andy Lau and Louis Koo, the two award-winning best actors star on opposing sides of a drug war. As a bounty of $100 million Hong Kong dollars is made to hunt down the biggest drug dealer in the city, Hong Kong becomes the battleground for the fight between good and evil.

programme.title: One Second
programme.desc: Directed by renowned director Zhang Yimou, the film is set during the Cultural Revolution, where a common man escapes a labour camp to find a newsreel that captures his daughter for one second in a movie. On the way, he encounters an orphan who also seeks the movie reel. Can the man finally pass the reel to a projectionist and screen the movie?

programme.title: Infernal Affairs III
programme.desc: Ming is transferred to do menial police work ten months after the murder of Yan, in 2004. Meanwhile, a new star, Wing, has emerged in the police force and Ming suspects he is also a mole sent by the triad. Determined to start anew, Ming must kill Wing while ensuring his own identity does not get exposed.

programme.title: Mother VS Mother
programme.desc: Guan De Xing fell in love with Li Xiao Yun when he was young, but was opposed by his mother and had to marry Zhou Shen Yu. Since then, Li holds a grudge against Zhou. Unfortunately, the son of Guan and Zhou falls in love with Li’s daughter, and as the two mothers meet, they start brawling again!

programme.title: HK Lan Kwai Fong
programme.desc: Lee is the Production head of an advertising firm who tries to improve her team’s performance by competing with Creative head Chan in the day and clubbing at Lan Kwai Fong for ideas at night. Lee runs into her ex-boyfriend before a big commercial shoot and drowns her sorrows drinking at Lan Kwai Fong, but finally picks herself up with Chan’s help.

programme.title: Wu Xia
programme.desc: Martial artist Liu hides his identity and lives in a remote village with his wife Ah Yu and their two sons, but somehow gets embroiled in a bizarre murder case. Constable Xu is a kung fu fanatic, whose curiosity forces Liu into a death duel with the Sect Leader of the 72 Demons, and puts Liu’s family and homeland in a great danger...

programme.title: Treasure Hunt
programme.desc: A commercial director Peggy shoots an ad on a deserted island while some mysterious men with the treasure map are also there to hunt for the hidden Ming Dynasty treasures. However, the map is stolen by Star who lives on the island. Star and Peggy unveil the hidden treasures but end up being chased by the mysterious men…

programme.title: From Vegas To Macau II
programme.desc: Mark, the chief accountant of a money-laundering syndicate, has stolen US$15 billion from the fund and absconded to Thailand with his daughter. Interpol agent Lok seeks help from Ken, the God of Gamblers, to capture the syndicate’s mastermind. As they search for Mark to testify in the case, Ken reunites with the love of his life…

programme.title: Flashover
programme.desc: This is based on a true story. A sudden earthquake hits the gas pipes in an industrial park, triggering massive explosions and engulfing the neighboring area in flames. When the Fire Rescue Force reaches the scene, firefighters must fight against the flames and time, as they commit to safeguard lives with their own.

programme.title: Distinction
programme.desc: A music teacher in a special needs school, an underachiever from an elite school, and a rebellious teenager with a handicapped brother take part in a campus musical for various reasons. Little did they know that this turns out to be a journey of self-discovery.

programme.title: Vanguard
programme.desc: A businessman Qin Guo Li is being kidnapped in London and his daughter is also in danger. The international security team, Vanguard, is hired to rescue them. Tang Huan Ting, the founder, gathers an elite team to track them down across countries, from London to Africa and Dubai. In the process, they also discover another dangerous conspiracy.

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: Mosaic, an urban sketcher, is suffering from ALS and wants to create some fond memories as his condition worsens. When Mosaic reunites with his old classmate Angelfish, whom he has a crush on since primary school, he asks her to fulfill his one last wish by becoming his girlfriend for just one day. Will Angelfish say “yes”?

programme.title: Caught in Time
programme.desc: Based on true events, Detective Zhong Cheng leads a task force in pursuit of Eagle, a criminal gang led by Zhang Sun. Highly methodical and disciplined, the gang manages to avoid capture after each heist. A decade later, the need to stop Eagle is more urgent than ever when Zhong Cheng realizes that his time is almost up to solve the case.

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: Shadows
programme.desc: Ching is a forensic psychiatrist who has the power to enter a person’s subconscious mind. In her latest case, she suspects that another psychiatrist is responsible for a brutal murder-cum-suicide case involving a social worker. In the investigation process, Ching finds herself under suspicion instead, as she comes face-to-face with a past trauma…

programme.title: First Love the Litter on the Breeze
programme.desc: This movie is the directorial debut of actor Eric Kot for Wong Kar Wai. Eric features the topic of first love in his first movie: a sleepwalker guided through the night by a lonely admirer is bizarre yet romantic, while a married grocer facing the vengeful first love that he once rejected is heartbreaking.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 2
programme.desc: In this sequel, Zhang Wu Ji successfully rescued the Six Major sects at Dadu. Nevertheless, the quest for the Dragon Sabre continues as Wu Ji and his three girlfriends set sail for Ice Fire Island. After a series of vicious fights, they finally unveil the secret behind the Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre.

programme.title: Tales from the Occult
programme.desc: The movie consists of three tales about the horrors lurking in dark corners of the city. A young pop star goes back into depression when spooky things happen in her new home; an online influencer performs live in a mall, but it ends up being a livestream of his death; the residents of a tenement building battle a mysterious figure in the stairwell.

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his family’s expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his family’s reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: Turns We Take
programme.desc: A spicy hot pot restaurant in Northeast China serves different types of customers every day. Amongst them are a sweet young couple, two wayward young men and a taxi driver. Despite being complete strangers to each other, their lives are intertwined by a traffic accident…

programme.title: Black Ransom
programme.desc: Mann, an accomplished police officer, has allowed his career to wane after his wife was murdered by the mafia. However, Mann is forced to return to his former glory when he is assigned to investigate a former police inspector suspected to be kidnapping mafia bosses and demanding ransoms in exchange for their lives.

programme.title: A Murder Erased
programme.desc: Police officer Choi is assigned to a death scene investigation where the deceased body had laid undiscovered for eight years. A prosecutor joins the investigation after Choi has identified the suspect, and finds Choi’s actions suspicious when all manner of inconsistencies come to light from his statement...

programme.title: See You Tomorrow
programme.desc: In this chaotic world, every city has its own "navigators" who can help solve various relationship issues. Bar owner Chen and his partner Guan are legendary navigators, but in the process of helping a girl Xiao Yu, they must also face their own problems in an epic act of self-discovery that brings their lives from towering highs to withering lows.

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: A newly engaged Hong Kong woman tries to rid herself of a secret sham marriage to a mainlander that she was paid for years ago, before she can get married for real. Winner of Best Original Film Score and Best New Director at the 39th Hong Kong Film Awards.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: Infamous real-life drug kingpin Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly built an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police who ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: From Vegas To Macau
programme.desc: Chow Yun Fat stars as "Magic Hands" Ken, a legendary gambling maestro who is forced out of retirement when his daughter's safety is compromised by an international gambling mafia. In order to save her, Ken and his new protégé Cool must work together to expose the evil mastermind by challenging him to a high stakes head-to-head battle of cards.

programme.title: Sound of Colors
programme.desc: Lonesome marriage consultant Ming meets a blind but charming young lady, Yeuk, at a subway station. When Ming suddenly turns blind too, Yeuk helps him navigate through his world of darkness, and they begin to fall in love. This feature is based on the illustrated book from famous Taiwan illustrator Jimmy Liao.

programme.title: Legally Declared Dead
programme.desc: Insurance agent Sean visits Tak and Ling's home to follow up on a case and is shocked to see their son's corpse hanging above him. He suspects them of murdering their son to claim the insurance money and decides to launch his own investigation. As he becomes obsessed over their guilt, his kind nature is used against him by the real perpetrator.

Lea memberikan pelajaran intensif dan sebagai balasannya, Jemi memberikan pengetahuan tentang masalah asmara kepada Lea.

programme.title: Kanan Kiri Ok 2
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang upaya penjodohan terhadap seorang tetangga baru, yaitu Vina oleh para tetangga-tetangganya karena dikhawatirkan akan membuat suami-suami mereka tidak aman. Banyolan berkisar pada kesalahpahaman yang sengaja diciptakan agar menimbulkan gelak tawa, terlebih lagi dengan hadirnya Doyok dan Kadir.

programme.title: Gentayangan
programme.desc: Abimanyu Karindra tak punya pilihan selain membawa istrinya, Sofia dan kedua anak mereka serta adiknya Sheila untuk menetap di hotel peninggalan orangtua di lembah gunung ratusan kilometer dari Jakarta, setelah dinyatakan bangkrut oleh pengadilan. Hotel Kaki Langit yang awalnya dianggap sebagai tempat tinggal yang nyaman dan tenang, berubah menjadi teror menakutkan hanya beberapa saat setelah keluarga Karindra mulai menempatinya.

programme.title: Bing Slamet Sibuk
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang Bing Slamet yang berhasil menaklukkan anak-anak keluarga Eddy Sud, orang yang mempekerjakannya, dengan kepandaiannya bernyanyi. Film ini juga sarat dengan lelucon dengan hadirnya grup Kwartet jaya.

programme.title: Roy Kiyoshi (The Untold Story)
programme.desc: Roy, yang punya kemampuan berinteraksi dengan makhluk gaib sangat frustrasi ketika Rani adiknya diculik setan. Roy merasa gagal melindungi adiknya. Tiga tahun kemudian, Sheila, pekerja LSM yang peduli dalam penanggulangan anak hilang diteror setan ketika sedang menangani kasus anak hilang secara misterius. Sheila sangat yakin bahwa kemunculan setan ini ada hubungannya dengan kasus yang sedang ditanganinya.

programme.title: Hotline 666
programme.desc: Menceritakan tentang Erza yang terperangkap di sebuah rumah angker. Erza merupakan pengantar pizza, saat dia mengantaran pizza ke sebuah rumah an ternyata dihuni oleh Sandra, Miko, dan Dara. Sosok yang awalnya hanyalah rekaan Erza menjadi nyata. Pintu rumah itu tertutup secara gaib. Erza terkunci di dalamnya.

programme.title: Pohon Keramat
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang keluarga yang diteror oleh hantu pohon besar yang ada di depan rumah baru mereka. Keganjilan demi keganjilan terus berlanjut dan selalu mengintai keluarga tersebut.

programme.title: Berangkat
programme.desc: Kisah tiga sekawan, yakni, Jano, Joana, dan Dika yang masing-masing memiliki personality dan hobi yang berbeda. Mereka melakukan road trip ke Kawah Ijen dan dilanjutkan ke Bali. Bermodalkan VW Combi tua mereka menyusuri beberapa kota di Jawa dengan banyak cerita.

programme.title: Mencari Hilal
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang Mahmud yang selalu ingin mengajarkan bahwa Islam itu adalah agama untuk semua persoalan hidup. Dalam perjalannya mencari hilal dengan caranya yang sederhana tanpa menelan biaya sampai milyaran rupiah yang selama ini dilakukan oleh pemerintah, langkahnya terhalang dengan anaknya bernama Heli. Heli selau melontarkan pikiran liberalnya hingga membuat Mahmud gerah.

programme.title: Kuntilanak 2 (2019)
programme.desc: Di film pertama, Dinda berhasil lolos dari teror kuntilanak. Ia kemudian berniat menemui Karmila yang diyakini sebagai ibu kandungnya. Sialnya, Dinda yang berangkat bersama adik dan temannya malah terjebak dalam rumah di tengah hutan. Kejanggalan mulai terjadi di rumah tersebut. Dinda harus kembali berhadapan dengan kuntilanak.

programme.title: Perempuan-Perempuan Liar
programme.desc: Dua penagih hutang sinting, Dom dan Mino, tak sengaja bertemu perempuan gila, Mey dan Cindy. Dom dan Mino terjebak permainan gila Mey dan Cindy. Mereka membawa kabur Mey dari pernikahan

programme.title: Soekarno
programme.desc: Soekarno berperan penting dalam kemerdekaan Indonesia, dengan dibantu sahabat-sahabatnya. Dalam kisah ini juga ada sosok perempuan yang selalu mendukung karir dari soekarno yaitu Inggit dan Fatmawati, konflik juga sempat terjadi dalam kisah asmara Soekarno. Hingga pada akhirnya Indonesia bisa merdeka pada tanggal 17 Agustus 1945 dengan ditandakan pembacaan proklamasi oleh Soekarno.

programme.title: Arwah Goyang Jupe Depe
programme.desc: Lilis yang dulunya berprofesi sebagai penari disebuah grup tari jaipong, harus kembali ke profesi lamanya karena tuntutan ekonomi keluarga. Suaminya korban PHK dan menganggur. Namun, Neneng yang sekarang menjadi bintang primadona di grup tari tersebut, merasa mendapatkan saingan. Karena dengan cepat, pengunjung kembali menyukai Lilis. Persaingan anatara keduanya pun terjadi.

programme.title: Pelet Kuntilanak
programme.desc: Karena terobsesi dengan kecantikan dan juga untuk membalaskan dendam kepada pria-pria yang memperkosanya, Pamela dan juga Tantri bersekutu dengan iblis. Mereka pergi ke dukun dan menggunakan pelet celana dalam pria. Namun keadaan berubah ketika mereka berdua justru mengalami teror dari mahluk gaib yang menyerang mereka.

programme.title: Cas Cis Cus
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang seorang nenek yang sepanjang cerita dicitrakan selalu marah-marah sebelum keinginannya dipenuhi, yaitu : Minta kaset video porno dan minta kawin lagi dengan tukang pijit langganannya. Bahkan ia sempat lari dari rumah, walaupun akhirnya kembali lagi.

programme.title: Darah Perawan Bulan Madu
programme.desc: Putra yang baru menikahi Amira berencana mengajak sang istri untuk berbulan madu di pulau pribadinya. Namun keanehan-keanehan mulai terjadi menghantui pasangan pengantin baru tersebut.

programme.title: Titisan Si Pitung
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang seorang pemuda yang berusaha keras untuk menumpas ketidakadilan di desanya yang diakibatkan oleh Darip dan Ramdani. Ia sampai menuntut ilmu di luar desa untuk dapat mengatasi dua orang tersebut. Sepulangnya dari mencari ilmu, ia menjadi orang yang sangat sakti, dan akhirnya ia bisa mengalahkan mereka.

programme.title: Jatuh Cinta Lagi
programme.desc: Lila adalah pengacara idealis yang suka membela perempuan teraniaya dan Andre adalah pengacara dengan kasus-kasus "kelas kakap". Keduanya bertemu dalam kasus perceraian seorang penyanyi dangdut

programme.title: Sang Pencerah
programme.desc: Sepulang dari Mekah, Darwis muda mengubah namanya menjadi Ahmad Dahlan. Seorang pemuda usia 21 tahun yang gelisah atas pelaksanaan syariat Islam yang melenceng ke arah sesat, Syirik dan Bid'ah.

programme.title: Si Manis Jembatan Ancol
programme.desc: Maryam, sosok perempuan yang mencari kebahagiaan saat rumah tangganya dengan lelaki bernama Roy berada di ambang kehancuran. Hadirnya sosok Yudha mampu membuat Maryam menemukan ketenangan. Namun, sebuah kejadian tragis harus menimpanya. Setelah itu legenda menyeramkan mulai tersebar.

programme.title: Ganesha
programme.desc: Ganesha, pemuda daerah yang mencoba mengadu nasib di kota, karena atas pengaruh temannya. Pada saat perjalanan, ia berhasil menggagalkan aksi pembajakan di bis yang ia tumpangi. Sang supir pun berterima kasih kepadanya dan mengangkatnya anak.

programme.title: Ricky Nakalnya Anak Muda
programme.desc: Ricky sangat terpukul dengan kematian pacarnya, Sita saat terjun payung. la jadi kacau, kerjanya cuma jalan-jalan dengan jip tua terbuka, kumpul-kumpul dengan gengnya, dan berkelahi.

programme.title: Pesan Dari Surga
programme.desc: Grup band beraliran rock, Topeng, yang seluruh personilnya beranggotakan lima anak muda, menghadapi berbagai problem cinta. Ketika permasalahan nyaris meledak, seorang korban kecelakaan yang selamat ini dalam kondisi koma tiba-tiba sadar dan membawa berbagai pesan dari surga.

programme.title: Senggol Bacok
programme.desc: Galang tempramental & tidak pernah takut apapun, namun ia harus mengendalikan emosinya untuk dapat memenangkan hati sang cewek idaman.

programme.title: Belahan Jiwa
programme.desc: Cerita tentang empat sahabat yang selalu setia bersama, dan ternyata mereka semua berhubungan dengan pria yang sama

programme.title: Cinta Tapi Beda
programme.desc: Menceritakan tentang sepasang kekasih yang berbeda keyakinan Diana dan Cahyo. Namun saat mereka mulai mencoba melanjutkan ke jenjang yang lebih serius, orang tua mereka sangat bertentangan dengan rencana ini. Hingga dilema mereka memuncak saat Diana dijodohkan oleh Oka pria pilihan ibunya.

programme.title: Tiga
programme.desc: Menceritakan tentang masa depan di tahun 2036. Dikisahkan oleh tiga sahabat bernama Alif, Lam dan Mim yang ditemukan dengan situasi dimana mereka harus berjuangan atas kebenaran masing-masing.

programme.desc: Cerita Andy dan Martin yang dikerjai oleh Robin dan membuat mereka berdua harus menyamar menjadi perempuan dengan maksud melarikan diri. Mereka menyelinap ke dalam rombongan artis yang akan tour. Berharap akan mendapatkan salah satu gadis-gadis itu membuat kelucuan itu terjadi.

programme.title: Susah Jaga Keperawanan Di Jakarta
programme.desc: Di sebuah desa kecil bernama Kandang Jago, Srinthil, punya mimpi hidup senang dan tinggal di kota metropolitan. Gadis-gadis kampung yang lain cuma tertawa dengar impian Srinthil. Hanya Kunil dan Centini teman Srinthil yang bisa telaten jadi pendengar. Mereka bertiga sudah berteman sejak kecil. Menolak perjodohan, tiga gadis kampung ini kabur ke kota dengan menumpang mobil pengangkut sayur. Tiga sekawan sampai ke kota metropolitan. Nasib mempertemukan tiga sekawan ini dengan Berta, wanita jadi-jadian yang berprofesi sebagai germo. Akhirnya ke tiga sekawan itu menerima dengan satu persyaratan: asal mereka tetap perawan.

programme.title: Membakar Matahari
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang Yanti yang hidupnya berubah sejak diperkosa kawanan penjahat dan dijadikan pelacur di jakarta. Tetapi ia bisa diselamatkan oleh pacarnya, Rachman sebelum ia terjerumus lebih jauh. Walaupun Yanti bekas pelacur, Rachman tetap menikahinya. Setelah belajar ilmu bela diri dari kakeknya Rachman, Yanti dan Rachman memutuskan untuk balas dendam kepada penjahat yang telah memperkosa Yanti
